project.name: week 4 color palettes/art
project.notes: This creates an image that is inspired by the work of Jackson Pollock. The confetti block works to create a multi colored design by creating several lines The colors are created using a rainbow color palette with colors ranging on a spectrum from 30-90 The block works by choosing a random line in a random orientation with a random hue on the color spectrum that was given 30-90 The polka dot block works similarly but rather than creating lines it creates a dot with a random color in the rainbow palette
